<h3 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Release:"=
>Release :&nbsp;</h3>
<p>The upgrade will be done as part of Janus timeframe.</p>
<h3 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Motivatio=
n:">Motivation :&nbsp;</h3>
<p>Spring 5 has reached its end-of-life and will no longer receive official=
 updates, bug fixes, or security patches. Upgrading to Spring 6 ensures con=
tinued support, maintenance, and improved security for our applications.</p=
>
<p><br></p>
<h3 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Milestone=
s:"><strong>Milestones :&nbsp;<br></strong></h3>
<p>On a high level there would be 4 milestones to complete a full release t=
o upgrade spring/springboot in API infra platform.</p>
<p><br></p>
