<h3 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-StepbySte=
pguidetomigratethecodetoSpring6.x"><strong><br>
   Step by Step guide to migrate the code to Spring6.x<br></strong></h3>
<p><br></p>
<p>Following repos have been upgraded to spring boot 3.x.</p>
<p>Below are the PRs raised by platform teams to update the correct depende=
ncies in various repos to make the code compatible with latest version of s=
