<p>GRPC controllers needs to consume the above dev-platform and service-par=
ent tags and ensure the code is built successfully.</p>
<p>Refer below PRs for reference only:&nbsp;</p>
<p>From cloud: <a href=3D"https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-cloud/pu=
ll/285/files" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.com/n=
utanix-core/ntnx-api-cloud/pull/285/files</a></p>
<p>From tasks: <a href=3D"https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-tasks/pu=
ll/357/" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.com/nutani=
x-core/ntnx-api-tasks/pull/357/</a></p>
<p>From data-policies: <a href=3D"https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-=
data-policies/pull/615" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://gi=
thub.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-data-policies/pull/615</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step0:Dev=
/Featurebranchcreation"><strong>Step 0 : Dev/Feature branch creation</stron=
g></h5>
<ol>
 <li data-uuid=3D"30d1f914-417c-42f5-9144-579a684e165e">Create a ticket and=
 link to Milestone 1 Epic ENG-852800.</li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"e37ec97c-f04a-44d3-a7af-669de0f5e70e">Create a custom dev=
-branch : <strong>spring-upgrade&nbsp;</strong> for development activity. U=
pdate CANAVERAL_PACKAGER_BRANCH to <strong>spring-upgrade in </strong>.circ=
leci/config.yaml. This branch will be eventually enabled for namespace merg=
ed. This branch will be used to generate a tag later by API infra team to p=
erform sanity testing with prism-service on PC/AOS</li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"214aeb38-d634-47e7-9bf8-e25485ef0ff2">Periodically rebase=
 <strong>spring-upgrade </strong><span>branch with </span><strong>main</str=
ong><span> to ensure the branch is updated.</span></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-NOTE:Dono=
tcreateapullrequesttomainyetfromspring-upgradebranchasthiswillbeusedtotrigg=
ernamespacemergelater."><span style=3D"color:#1f845a;"><strong>NOTE : Do no=
t create a pull request to main yet from spring-upgrade branch as this will=
 be used to trigger namespace merge later.</strong></span></h2>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step1:Upd=
atingtheversionsofserviceparent,dev-platformandplatformtoolsasperabovetable=
."><strong>Step 1 :&nbsp;Updating the versions of service parent, dev-platf=
orm and platform tools as per above table.</strong></h5>
<p><br></p>
<ul>
 <li data-uuid=3D"0f4f5ddd-0ffe-420c-b842-390aeb26e43a">On updating the ser=
vice-parent, devtools and dev-platform the pom dependencies will start comp=
laining.<br><br>
  <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
   <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
    <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"b=
rush: java; gutter: false">[ERROR] The build could not read 3 projects -&gt=
; [Help 1]
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp;
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp; The project com.nutanix.nutanix-core.ntnx-api.iam:iam-j=
ava-dto-definitions:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT (/Users/manu.malhotra/nutanix/ntnx-api-=
iam/iam-api-external/iam-api-codegen/iam-java-dto-definitions/pom.xml) has =
1 error
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 'dependencies.dependency.version' for javax=
.validation:validation-api:jar is missing. @ line 16, column 17
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp;
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp; The project com.nutanix.nutanix-core.ntnx-api.iam:iam-j=
ava-client-sdk:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT (/Users/manu.malhotra/nutanix/ntnx-api-iam/i=
am-api-external/iam-api-codegen/iam-java-client-sdk/pom.xml) has 1 error
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 'dependencies.dependency.version' for org.a=
pache.httpcomponents:httpclient:jar is missing. @ line 44, column 17
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp;
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp; The project com.nutanix.nutanix-core.ntnx-api.iam:iam-s=
torage-utils:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT (/Users/manu.malhotra/nutanix/ntnx-api-iam/iam=
-api-external/iam-storage-utils/pom.xml) has 1 error
[ERROR]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 'dependencies.dependency.version' for javax=
.servlet:javax.servlet-api:jar is missing. @ line 22, column 21
[ERROR]
[ERROR]   The project com.nutanix.nutanix-core.ntnx-api.tasks:tasks-api-cod=
egen:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT (/Users/keshav.jindal/Desktop/ntnx-api-tasks/tasks-api=
-codegen/pom.xml) has 1 error
[ERROR]     'dependencies.dependency.version' for javax.annotation:javax.an=
notation-api:jar is missing. @ line 38, column 17</pre>
   </div>
  </div></li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"6fece7f9-349d-4f0b-a083-7c9912e79c9c">Update javax.valida=
tion:validation-api to *-api-codegen/pom.xml<br><br>
  <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
   <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
    <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"b=
rush: java; gutter: false">&lt;dependency&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;jakarta.validation&lt;/groupId&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;jakarta.validation-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
   </div>
  </div></li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"9063744f-e40b-4e9e-86d1-699370ec1fdb"><span style=3D"font=
-size: 14.0px;letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Add</span><span style=3D"font-size: 1=
4.0px;letter-spacing: 0.0px;"> org.apache.httpcomponents:httpclient depende=
ncy. This will be part of service-parent and will be managed in the BOM<br>=
<br></span>
  <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
   <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
    <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"b=
rush: xml; gutter: false">&lt;dependency&gt;&nbsp;=20
  &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.httpcomponents.client5&lt;/groupId&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;httpclient5&lt;/artifactId&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
   </div>
  </div></li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"feef9fa3-6580-497a-b5fc-80f0de28cc60">Update javax.valida=
tion:validation-api to below<br><br>
  <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
   <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
    <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"b=
rush: java; gutter: false">&lt;dependency&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;jakarta.validation&lt;/groupId&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;jakarta.validation-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
   </div>
  </div></li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"71520c5e-02db-446f-aed6-bea4ceec2cb1"><span>Update&nbsp;<=
/span>javax.annotation:javax.annotation-api to below<br><br>
  <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
   <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
    <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"b=
rush: java; gutter: false">&lt;dependency&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=20
&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;jakarta.annotation&lt;/groupId&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;jakarta.annotation-api&lt;/artifactId&=
gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
   </div>
  </div><br>
  <p>Javax dependencies no longer work with latest spring. The dependencies=
 will be migrated to use Jakarta specific artifacts.</p></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step2.Jav=
axtojakartausingthereplacerplugininpom.xmlingeneratedcode."><span><strong>S=
tep 2. Javax to jakarta using the replacer plugin in pom.xml in generated c=
ode.<br><br></strong></span></h5>
<ul>
 <li data-uuid=3D"d7c2e9a0-5223-4626-85d8-7ad6a45056b8"><span>The generated=
 java classes are still going to generate with `javax`. This needs to be re=
placed with jakarta.&nbsp;</span></li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"f2743b7c-b8b7-49c3-8da9-2b7d63b6d713"><span>The replacer =
plugin needs to be added in pom.xml of below modules:</span>
  <ul>
   <li data-uuid=3D"d1be8941-5478-423f-a92e-7d38a45da002"><span>spring-mvc-=
interfaces</span></li>
   <li data-uuid=3D"efe22b8d-4312-40d1-960d-5b4fc4e259e5"><span>java-client=
-sdk</span></li>
  </ul></li>
</ul>
<p><span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>
<p><span>&nbsp;Add the following maven plugin to the pom.xml file</span></p=
>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">&lt;plugin&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;com.google.code.maven-replacer-plugin&lt;/groupId&gt=
;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;replacer&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;1.5.3&lt;/version&gt;
        &lt;executions&gt;
          &lt;!-- Execution 1: After initial code generation --&gt;
          &lt;execution&gt;
            &lt;id&gt;replace-javax-process-sources&lt;/id&gt;
            &lt;phase&gt;generate-sources&lt;/phase&gt;
            &lt;goals&gt;
              &lt;goal&gt;replace&lt;/goal&gt;
            &lt;/goals&gt;
            &lt;configuration&gt;
              &lt;includes&gt;
                &lt;include&gt;${project.build.directory}/generated-sources=
/swagger/src/**/*.java&lt;/include&gt;
              &lt;/includes&gt;
              &lt;excludes&gt;
                &lt;exclude&gt;${project.build.directory}/generated-sources=
/swagger/src/**/ApiClient.java&lt;/exclude&gt;
                &lt;exclude&gt;${project.build.directory}/generated-sources=
/swagger/src/**/MutualTLSConfig.java&lt;/exclude&gt;
              &lt;/excludes&gt;
              &lt;replacements&gt;
                &lt;replacement&gt;
                  &lt;token&gt;@javax.validation.constraints&lt;/token&gt;
                  &lt;value&gt;@jakarta.validation.constraints&lt;/value&gt=
;
                &lt;/replacement&gt;
                &lt;replacement&gt;
                  &lt;token&gt;import javax.validation.constraints&lt;/toke=
n&gt;
                  &lt;value&gt;import jakarta.validation.constraints&lt;/va=
lue&gt;
                &lt;/replacement&gt;
                &lt;replacement&gt;
                  &lt;token&gt;javax.validation&lt;/token&gt;
                  &lt;value&gt;jakarta.validation&lt;/value&gt;
                &lt;/replacement&gt;
                &lt;replacement&gt;
                  &lt;token&gt;javax.servlet&lt;/token&gt;
                  &lt;value&gt;jakarta.servlet&lt;/value&gt;
                &lt;/replacement&gt;
                &lt;replacement&gt;
                  &lt;token&gt;javax.ws.rs&lt;/token&gt;
                  &lt;value&gt;jakarta.ws.rs&lt;/value&gt;
                &lt;/replacement&gt;
                &lt;replacement&gt;
                  &lt;token&gt;@javax&lt;/token&gt;
                  &lt;value&gt;@jakarta&lt;/value&gt;
                &lt;/replacement&gt;
              &lt;/replacements&gt;
            &lt;/configuration&gt;
          &lt;/execution&gt;
        &lt;/executions&gt;
      &lt;/plugin&gt;</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step3.Rep=
lacetheAOSutildependencytoincludeonlyprotoandbasequalifier"><strong>Step 3.=
 Replace the AOS util dependency to include only proto and base qualifier</=
strong></h5>
<p><span>With the spring upgrade efforts platform team has refactored some =
code from gerrit and added a new module http-utils in ntnx-api-utils. Contr=
oller teams leveraging the platform utility need to replace the existing de=
pendency of<strong> aos-util</strong> &nbsp;with below dependencies with re=
spective classifiers<br><br><strong>From :</strong></span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;util&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>To :&nbsp;</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;util&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;classifier&gt;proto&lt;/classifier&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;util&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;classifier&gt;base&lt;/classifier&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;Ensure you do not pull the<strong> </strong>uber<strong> util.jar.=
</strong> Check this by verifying the dependency tree</p>
<p>Command to capture the dependency tree :</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">mvn dependency:tree -s settings.xml | tee output.t=
x</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">nitish.khune@C02FX3NJML85 ntnx-api-utils % grep "a=
os-util" output.tx=20
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:proto:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT:=
provided
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:proto:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT:=
compile
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:base:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT:c=
ompile
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:proto:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT:=
compile
[INFO] |  +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:base:17.6.0-SNAPSHO=
T:compile
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:proto:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT:=
compile
[INFO] |  +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:base:17.6.0-SNAPSHO=
T:compile
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:proto:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT:=
compile
[INFO] |  +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:base:17.6.0-SNAPSHO=
T:compile
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:proto:17.6.0-SNAPSHOT:=
compile
nitish.khune@C02FX3NJML85 ntnx-api-utils % </pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><br><br>
  The controller <strong>should not have</strong> below dependency pulled i=
n the mvn dependency tree</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">nitish.khune@C02FX3NJML85 ntnx-api-utils % grep "a=
os-util" output.tx-old=20
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:17.6.0.1757908535:prov=
ided
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:17.6.0.1757908535:comp=
ile
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:17.6.0.1757908535:comp=
ile
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:17.6.0.1757908535:comp=
ile
[INFO] +- com.nutanix.nutanix-core.aos-util:util:jar:17.6.0.1757908535:comp=
ile</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step4.Rep=
eatinsourcecode,manually"><strong><span>Step 4. Repeat in source code, manu=
ally</span></strong></h5>
<p><span>Repeat this where ever you have javax. All the traces of javax sho=
uld be moved to jakarta. The above plugin should not directly replace javax=
 with jakarta. It should be something like `javax.validation` to `jakarta.v=
alidation`</span></p>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step5.Htt=
pclient5changes."><strong><span>Step 5. Httpclient5 changes.</span></strong=
></h5>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span><span>The client code relying on httpclient should be=
 updated to httpclient5. Http client connection mechanism is now upgraded t=
o use httpclient5 library.</span></p>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span>Sample code changes are :</span></p>
<p><span>&nbsp;<span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper"><img class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" src=3D"cedf8c776ca37bb14=
d8a6546995b1affc48cba9a90c404d5d7202a9c99ddad4a" data-image-src=3D"/downloa=
d/attachments/468284426/image-2025-10-15_10-47-59.png?version=3D1&amp;modif=
icationDate=3D1760550439386&amp;api=3Dv2" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"=
0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"468284427" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1"=
 data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alia=
s=3D"image-2025-10-15_10-47-59.png" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.eng=
.nutanix.com:8443" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-lin=
ked-resource-container-id=3D"468284426" data-linked-resource-container-vers=
ion=3D"106" tabindex=3D"0" alt=3D"" width=3D"468" height=3D"373"></span></s=
pan></p>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Step 6</strong>: Upgrade swagger-request validator <strong=
>2.46.0</strong>. There are many controllers directly dependent on swagger-=
request-validator modules.</span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">&lt;dependency&gt;
   &lt;artifactId&gt;swagger-request-validator-springmvc&lt;/artifactId&gt;
   &lt;groupId&gt;com.atlassian.oai&lt;/groupId&gt;
   &lt;version&gt;2.46.0&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step7.Tes=
tFailuresneedtobefixed"><strong><span>Step 7. Test Failures need to be fixe=
d</span></strong></h5>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span>For the tests TestNG is used, however the junit jars are getting p=
ulled in into the test runtime with the latest spring-boot-starter-test.</s=
pan></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span>The spring-boot-starter-test pom.xml dependency should be upated.<=
/span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">&lt;dependency&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-test&lt;/artifactId&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;exclusions&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;exclusion&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;ch.qos.logback&lt;/groupId&gt=
;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;logback-classic&lt;/artifa=
ctId&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/exclusion&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;exclusion&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/=
groupId&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-loggin=
g&lt;/artifactId&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/exclusion&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;exclusion&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;org.junit.jupiter&lt;/groupId=
&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;junit-jupiter&lt;/artifact=
Id&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/exclusion&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;exclusion&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;org.mockito&lt;/groupId&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;mockito-junit-jupiter&lt;/=
artifactId&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/exclusion&gt;
&nbsp; &lt;/exclusions&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step8:Ens=
urecompilationsucceedincircleci."><strong>Step 8 : Ensure compilation succe=
ed in circle ci.</strong></h5>
<p>Teams to confirm the compilation of their respective feature branches in=
 circleci. NOTE : there could be failures related to push to elements step =
which can be ignored for now. The feature branch must be treated as any rel=
ease branch and direct push to this branch should be prohibited.</p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Step9:Upd=
atetheinternalnutanixsdkswithspringcompatibleversions"><strong>Step 9 : Upd=
ate the internal nutanix sdks with spring compatible versions</strong></h5>
<p>Some controllers internally depend on java SDKs generated by other inter=
nal nutanix sdks. Service teams depending on these internal sdks need to co=
ordinate and make sure that the spring6 compiled SDKs are consumed in their=
 controllers&nbsp;<br><br>
  Upon doing global search below are some sdk dependencies observed&nbsp;</=
p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
  <colgroup>
   <col>
   <col>
  </colgroup>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Co=
ntrolllers</strong></td>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Ja=
va SDK dependencies</strong></td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">pcdr-pc</t=
d>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">pcdr-pe-sd=
k and lcm-sdks</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">pcdr-pe</t=
d>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">pcdr-pc</t=
d>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">diskmgmt</=
td>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">categories=
</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">flow</td>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">categories=
</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">volumes</t=
d>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">prism</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">categories=
</td>
    <td style=3D"vertical-align: bottom;" class=3D"confluenceTd">iam</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-TestingJa=
vaSDKslocally:">Testing Java SDKs locally:</h3>
<ul>
 <li data-uuid=3D"e3d1685d-6c7a-4e0d-a5d2-28eb6817bc06">Clone the repo: <a =
href=3D"https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-sdk-tests" class=3D"extern=
al-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-sdk-test=
s</a>
  <ul>
   <li data-uuid=3D"575e350f-a111-4206-a0fa-1e96450086c7">Checkout to kj-te=
st branch: <a href=3D"https://github.com/nutanix-core/ntnx-api-sdk-tests/tr=
ee/kj-test" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.com/nut=
anix-core/ntnx-api-sdk-tests/tree/kj-test</a></li>
   <li data-uuid=3D"1b4e968b-0e62-40aa-bc54-c11155f0b422">This repository c=
an be used by service teams to test the generated SDKs locally. (Note: It=
=E2=80=99s still in early phase.)</li>
  </ul></li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"2fa0d364-66d4-4801-9aa3-e03da911afad">Changes in pom.xml=
=20
  <ul>
   <li data-uuid=3D"d30455dd-4f9b-47c2-9667-fb0d1878da24">Each service SDK =
(for example, tasks-java-client, vmm-java-client, etc.) has a corresponding=
 &lt;dependency&gt; block in the pom.xml file, but they are <strong>comment=
ed</strong> out by default.=20
    <ul>
     <li data-uuid=3D"f2572e4b-a2a2-4286-a579-1878c3aea115">Uncomment the d=
ependency block for your specific SDK.</li>
     <li data-uuid=3D"8c0a02d8-f9eb-4041-8a17-4703dbd0dfae">Update the syst=
emPath to point to the location of your locally built SDK JAR file.&nbsp;<b=
r>
      <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
       <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
        <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=
=3D"brush: java; gutter: false">        &lt;dependency&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;com.nutanix.api&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;tasks-java-client&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;17.6.0-SNAPSHOT&lt;/version&gt;
            &lt;scope&gt;system&lt;/scope&gt;
            &lt;systemPath&gt;/Users/keshav.jindal/Desktop/ntnx-api-tasks/t=
asks-api-codegen/tasks-java-client-sdk/target/tasks-java-client-sdk-17.6.0-=
SNAPSHOT.jar&lt;/systemPath&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>
       </div>
      </div></li>
    </ul></li>
  </ul></li>
 <li data-uuid=3D"216ec56a-3eac-41c4-b263-8c932f342831">Changes in Main.jav=
a=20
  <ul>
   <li data-uuid=3D"e19ef35d-45ad-4973-ab11-d83ee3665b48">File path: /ntnx-=
api-sdk-tests/java/test/src/main/java/org/example/Main.java</li>
   <li data-uuid=3D"5f0bbab5-58e5-493f-8e55-c7c6045e6734">Add your PC host =
by updating this line<br>
    <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
     <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
      <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D=
"brush: java; gutter: false">public static final String HOST =3D "10.55.64.=
60"; // Replace this with your PC IP</pre>
     </div>
    </div></li>
   <li data-uuid=3D"a1bfc0ba-993b-43fd-bc33-bd4f0c0fa0fe">Write a test func=
tion for your API (for example, prismTest()), and then call it from the mai=
n() function.</li>
   <li data-uuid=3D"b999fcb6-8265-435c-90ae-ae8dbb63a4ad">You might get som=
e import errors after writing your test case. Example fixes: We need to upd=
ate pri to tsks (Reason: these are task specific APIs, and not generated vi=
a namespace merge pipeline.)<br>
    <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
     <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
      <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D=
"brush: java; gutter: false">// from:
import com.nutanix.dp1.pri.prism.v4.config.ListTasksApiResponse;
import com.nutanix.pri.java.client.api.TasksApi;


// to:
import com.nutanix.dp1.tsks.prism.v4.config.ListTasksApiResponse;
import com.nutanix.tsks.java.client.api.TasksApi;</pre>
     </div>
    </div></li>
  </ul></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-Reference=
s">References</h3>
<ul>
 <li><a href=3D"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/wiki/Spring-=
Boot-3.0-Migration-Guide" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://=
github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/wiki/Spring-Boot-3.0-Migration-Guide=
</a><strong><br><br></strong><strong>NOTE : You may use cursor to migrate s=
ome of the code to use Springboot 3 /Spring 6.2.x constructs.&nbsp;</strong=
></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color:#ae2e24;">Please post any question in <strong>#adon=
is-springboot-issues&nbsp;</strong>channel. &nbsp;One of the developers can=
 address any concerns raised in the slack.</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<h5 id=3D"MigrationguideforSpringframeworkupgradeforV4APIplatform-FAQs:">FA=
Qs:&nbsp;</h5>
<ol>
 <li data-uuid=3D"cbb613a0-7245-43c2-ae8e-56b181045722">Issue : TestResttem=
plate default configurations are changed in spring6. There might be unexpec=
ted failures in integration test.<br>
   Resolution : &nbsp;Disable the default retries to ensure the APIs are no=
t invoked again in case of certain failures.<br>
  <div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
   <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
    <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"b=
rush: java; gutter: false">      testRestTemplate.getRestTemplate().setRequ=
estFactory(new HttpComponentsClientHttpRequestFactory(HttpClients.custom().=
disableAutomaticRetries().build()));</pre>
   </div>
  </div></li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
    </div>
</body>
